      "kind": "content",
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "You can use a value function to specify the individual components of an animated transform."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "For example, to create a basic animation that rotates a layer from 0° to 180° around its z-axis, you would create a "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/quartzcore/cabasicanimation"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " object with a "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/quartzcore/cabasicanimation/1412519-fromvalue"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " of "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "0"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ", a "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/quartzcore/cabasicanimation/1412523-tovalue"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " of "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/swift/float/1845969-pi"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ", and a "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/quartzcore/capropertyanimation/1412447-valuefunction"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " of a "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/quartzcore/cavaluefunction"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " with a function name of "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/quartzcore/kcavaluefunctionrotatez"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The value functions "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/quartzcore/kcavaluefunctionscale"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " and "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/quartzcore/kcavaluefunctiontranslate"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " require 3 values, for the individual "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "x"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ", "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "y"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " and "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "z"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " components. When working with these value functions, you specify the animation's "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/quartzcore/cabasicanimation/1412519-fromvalue"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " and "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/quartzcore/cabasicanimation/1412523-tovalue"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " as arrays."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
